obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (39798)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `1. 1st September, 1953, vide notification No. S. R.O. 1624, dated 26th August, 1953, see Gazette of India, Part II, s. 3.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39798&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Scheduled Areas (Assimilation`
  line `of Laws) Act, 1953.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (39799)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39799&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act,—`
  line
  line `(a) "appointed day" means the date appointed under sub-section (2) of section 1 for the coming`
  line `into force of this Act;.`
  line
  line `(b) "law" means so much of any Act, Ordinance, Regulation, rule, order or bye-law as relates to`
  line `any of the matters enumerated in Lists I and III in the Seventh Schedule to the Constitution.`
  line
  line `(c) "scheduled areas" mean the areas specified in the Schedule.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (39800)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Assimilation of laws.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39800&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1) All laws which immediately before the appointed day extend to, or are`
  line `in force in, the scheduled areas shall on that day cease to be in force in the scheduled areas except as`
  line `respects things done or omitted to be done before that day, and for the removal of doubts, it is hereby`
  line `declared that section 6 of the General Clauses Act, 1897 (10 of 1897) shall apply in relation to such cesser`
  line `as it applies in relation to the repeal of an enactment by a Central Act.`
  line
  line `(2) All laws which immediately before the appointed day extend to, or are in force in, the district of`
  line `Nowgong in the State of Assam shall as from that day extend to, or, as the case may be, come into force`
  line `in, the areas specified in paragraph 1 of the Schedule.`
  line
  line `(3) All laws which immediately before the appointed day extend to, or are in force in, the district of`
  line `Sibsagar in the State of Assam shall as from that day extend to, or, as the case may be, come into force in,`
  line `the areas specified in paragraph 2 of the Schedule.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (39801)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Transitional provisions.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39801&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in section 3, the Central`
  line `Government or the Government of the State of Assam may, by order, direct that during such period, not`
  line `exceeding twelve months from the appointed day, as may be specified in the order, any law which`
  line `immediately before the appointed day was in force in the scheduled areas, shall be deemed to have`
  line `continued to be in force therein or any specified part thereof, and may further likewise direct that any law`
  line `which would have extended to, or come into force in, the scheduled areas on the appointed day, shall not`
  line `be deemed to have extended thereto or come into force therein or any specified part thereof.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (39802)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title Savings.
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39802&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in section 3, all suits, cases and other legal`
  line `proceedings between parties all of whom belong to the Scheduled Tribes specified in item 2 of Part`
  line `I—Assam, of the Schedule annexed to the Constitution (Scheduled Tribes) Order, 1950 or such other`
  line `tribe or tribes, as may be specified in this behalf, shall be tried and continue to be tried under the Rules for`
  line `the Administration of Justice and Police in the Sibsagar and Nowgong Mikir Hills Tracts as if this Act has`
  line `not been passed.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (39803)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Provision for removal of difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382&sectionId=39803&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_24_00025_195316_1517807328382
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `If any difficulty arises in relation to the transition under`
  line `section 3 from one law or group of laws to another law or group of laws, the Central Government may, by`
  line `order notified in the Official Gazette, make such provision as it considers necessary for the removal of the`
  line difficulty.
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
